OL,3,CCovid Inquiry report: Paramedic's
OL,4,Cwidow calls government 'disgusting'
OL,6,FBy Laurence Griffin, Production
OL,7,FJournalist
OL,9,FThe widow of a paramedic from
OL,10,FNottinghamshire who died during Covid
OL,11,Fis among those who have reacted to a
OL,12,Fpublic inquiry report, which found the
OL,13,Fgovernment "failed its citizens" by
OL,14,Fbeing ill-prepared for Covid.
OL,16,FJulie Goodwin from Bilsthorpe in
OL,17,FNottinghamshire lost her husband to
OL,18,FCovid.
