OL,3,CCovid Inquiry report: Paramedic's
OL,4,Cwidow calls government 'disgusting'
OL,6,FCharlie Goodwin was on the front line
OL,7,Fof the fight against the pandemic
OL,8,Fworking as a paramedic, and died in
OL,9,FApril 2020 - just weeks after the
OL,10,Fcountry went into lockdown.
OL,12,FBaroness Hallet, chair of the UK Covid-
OL,13,F19 Inquiry's first report, has today
OL,14,Furged the Labour government to
OL,15,Fimplement urgent and "fundamental
OL,16,Freform" and warned another pandemic is
OL,17,Flikely in the near to medium future.
OL,19,F"He could've been saved if things had
OL,20,Fbeen done right"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
