OL,3,CCovid Inquiry report: Paramedic's
OL,4,Cwidow calls government 'disgusting'
OL,6,FJulie said: "I don't think (the
OL,7,Fgovernment) were prepared at all. They
OL,8,Flocked down too late and opened up too
OL,9,Fsoon.
OL,11,F"If they had the right equipment and
OL,12,Fenough equipment there would have been
OL,13,Fa lot of lives saved."
OL,15,F"My husband was on the front line but
OL,16,Fhe thought he was safe in that PPE -
OL,17,Fthey brought it in eventually but it
OL,18,Fwas just a plastic apron and gloves
OL,19,Fand an everyday mask.
