OL,3,CCovid Inquiry report: Paramedic's
OL,4,Cwidow calls government 'disgusting'
OL,6,F"It's disgusting - he could have been
OL,7,Fsaved if things had been done right."
OL,9,FBirmingham GP Dr Anita Raja gave birth
OL,10,Fin the midst of the pandemic in 2020
OL,11,Fand said a lack of PPE left her and
OL,12,Fher youngest son "highly vulnerable."
OL,14,FShe said: "We were still doing nursing
OL,15,Fvisits, we were doing home visits of
OL,16,Freally unwell vulnerable people
OL,17,Fwithout PPE.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
