OL,3,CCovid Inquiry report: Paramedic's
OL,4,Cwidow calls government 'disgusting'
OL,6,F"I didn't have PPE for a whole month,
OL,7,Fin fact we didn't even know what PPE
OL,8,Fwhat it was during that time, GP's
OL,9,Fsurgeries didn't stock any masks and
OL,10,Fit was really new."
OL,12,FLady Hallet said: "It is not a
OL,13,Fquestion of 'if' another pandemic will
OL,14,Fstrike but 'when'" as she called on
OL,15,Fthe government to be equally as
OL,16,Fprepared for another health crisis as
OL,17,Fit would be for a potential war.
