OL,3,CCovid Inquiry report: Paramedic's
OL,4,Cwidow calls government 'disgusting'
OL,6,FHer report concluded "the processes,
OL,7,Fplanning and policy of the civil
OL,8,Fcontingency structures within the UK
OL,9,Fgovernment and devolved
OL,10,Fadministrations and civil services
OL,11,Ffailed their citizens."
OL,13,FAmong her criticisms were:
OL,15,F"I can't thank the government at that
OL,16,Ftime enough for what they did for us."
