OL,3,CCovid Inquiry report: Paramedic's
OL,4,Cwidow calls government 'disgusting'
OL,6,FDespite that report, Sarah Jones, who
OL,7,Fruns Cedars Care Home in Stourbridge,
OL,8,Fsaid she received "fantastic support"
OL,9,Ffrom the government, which she
OL,10,Fbelieves did all it could in the
OL,11,Fcircumstances.
OL,13,FShe said: "I know I've heard other
OL,14,Fstories but we were given unlimited
OL,15,Fsupplies of PPE, we were given grants
OL,16,Fand they would pay for agency staff if
OL,17,Fwe couldn't get staff in so I can't
OL,18,Fthank the government at that time
OL,19,Fenough for what they did for us."
