OL,3,CCovid Inquiry report: Paramedic's
OL,4,Cwidow calls government 'disgusting'
OL,6,FAnswering Lady Hallet's call for
OL,7,Fpreparation, Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,8,FStarmer has said the Government will
OL,9,F"carefully consider the
OL,10,Frecommendations" of the inquiry.
OL,12,FHe said "The Government's first
OL,13,Fresponsibility is to keep the public
OL,14,Fsafe, and as Prime Minister I am
OL,15,Fpersonally committed to each and every
OL,16,Ffamily that lost loved ones, and whose
OL,17,Flives were changed forever, that this
OL,18,FGovernment will learn the lessons from
OL,19,Fthe Inquiry"
